From 9c40b9cae4d6e6520fb0986a1fd1deec925fa262 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <quic_pnandesh@quicinc.com>
Date: Thu, 27 Mar 2025 19:54:49 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 1/8] wifi: ath12k: Reorganize ath12k directory structure

Reorganize ath12k directory structure to facilitate
the unified driver design, by moving wifi7
specific files hal_desc.h, hal_rx.c, hal_rx.h, hal_tx.c,
hal_tx.h, rx_desc.h to wifi7 directory, as the architecture specific
component is moving to the new directory.
The moved .c files will continue to be part of ath12k.ko
temporarily until the corresponding infra for movement
to the ath12k_wifi7.ko arrives in upcoming patches.

Tested-on: QCN9274 hw2.0 PCI WLAN.WBE.1.3.1-00173-QCAHKSWPL_SILICONZ-1
Tested-on: WCN7850 hw2.0 PCI WLAN.HMT.1.0.c5-00481-QCAHMTSWPL_V1.0_V2.0_SILICONZ-3

Signed-off-by: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <quic_pnandesh@quicinc.com>
